{"tid":1368792,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我個仔琴日翻學就比老師要求轉校","createTime":"2019-07-26T14:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T14:38:30.000Z","uid":146358,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"80fc474b6e71f38143a2cd79187a8decb16a9820","tid":1368792,"uid":146358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:29:18.000Z","msg":"笑下啦香港人 你地都好攰啦<br />\n<br />\n是咁的<br />\n<br />\n琴日我個仔第一日返幼稚園<br />\n正常一返到去冇咗老豆老母細路喊都係好正常<br />\n但係我個仔喊都冇喊<br />\n老師讚佢叻仔之後就去氹其他細路<br />\n<br />\n當其他細路慢慢開始唔喊靜落嚟嘅時候<br />\n我個仔講咗句<br />\n「我地爸爸媽媽唔要我地喇」<br />\n<br />\n成個幼稚園瞬間失控<br />\n<br />\n老師第二次氹返啲細路<br />\n當啲細路開始喊到勊開始停嘅時候<br />\n我個仔無啦啦又爆咗句<br />\n「我地會俾人賣咗去，以後見唔返爸爸媽媽喇」<br />\n<br />\n一瞬間全部小朋友都喊到不似人形<br />\n有啲仲喊到差啲窒息<br />\n搞到老師就嚟痴線<br />\n最後將佢調位調到最後面<br />\n<br />\n辛辛苦苦終於捱到食飯時間<br />\n<br />\n我個仔收到個飯之後大大力推咗落地<br />\n「唔係媽媽煮嘅我唔食！」<br />\n<br />\n之後所有細路有樣學樣將啲飯推哂落地<br />\n又喊住又搵媽媽<br />\n<br />\n等到放學嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n我個仔第一個沖咗出嚟比我接<br />\n突然一個擰頭向住其他細路講<br />\n「我地聽日都會再俾人送過嚟架」<br />\n<br />\n嗰個畫面<br />\n我一世都唔會忘記有幾壯觀"},{"pid":"5f1a8466b96c405b9ece43afab2f45306c9ed808","tid":1368792,"uid":217844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed8c64ae1d1df1bce70fcaea8bd65eb77a31db02","tid":1368792,"uid":146358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f1a8466b96c405b9ece43afab2f45306c9ed808","tid":1368792,"uid":217844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:31:23.000Z","msg":"雖然篇野都po過幾次 但真心好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放鬆下啦香港人"},{"pid":"83eb9fa75e28536e42c069ec5bdcc1f733493e97","tid":1368792,"uid":217844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed8c64ae1d1df1bce70fcaea8bd65eb77a31db02","tid":1368792,"uid":146358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f1a8466b96c405b9ece43afab2f45306c9ed808","tid":1368792,"uid":217844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:31:23.000Z","msg":"雖然篇野都po過幾次 但真心好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放鬆下啦香港人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:34:08.000Z","msg":"真係好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb7327e8bafe9cbe3ba9f93a515d438b626cabb","tid":1368792,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:38:30.000Z","msg":"又loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}